channel.title: Farming patch name dissapears
channel.description:
Hello there i'm stuck with an issue. When i use a rake on the farming patch, the weed is raked of and leaves an empty patch. But the patch name dissapears after that, it's a nameless object so i can't use on 'patch'.
Perhaps anyone knows how to fix this? thanks.
